+                LINK_ADDRESS.getDescription(),
+                LINK_PORT.getDescription(),
+                LINK_TIMEOUTMS.getDescription());
+    }
+
+    @Override
+    public String getTitle() {
+        return "Properties handling forked VMs. Modify only if you are sure what youa re doing";
+    }
